Module com.example.studiomanagergui
Package com.example.studiomanagergui

Class MemberList

java.lang.Object
com.example.studiomanagergui.MemberList
public class MemberList extends Object
The MemberList class manages a list of fitness club members. It provides methods for adding, removing, and loading members, as well as sorting and printing the list based on different criteria.
Author:
Priyansh Parikh, Siddarth Seloth
